{"tid":1670841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市急轉熱】沙田第一城三日連反四口價","createTime":"2019-10-23T06:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T07:55:47.000Z","uid":35950,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bec8d72d60ed0faafa32814ed3ee80cd8f617f2f","tid":1670841,"uid":35950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"施政報告後二手市場氣氛急升溫，業主叫價亦紛紛回揚。沙田第一城有兩房放盤，一直叫價540萬元放售，近日業主見各區交投激增，竟在三日連反四口價。最新開價570萬元，以實用面積284方呎計，呎價重上2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191023/bkn-20191023112202589-1023_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20191023%2Fbkn-20191023112202589-1023_00842_001.html&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=9e8d7834\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191023/bkn-20191023112202589-1023_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭幫大家上車，施政報告後樓價大反彈，有能力真係盡快入市，一眾炒樓司局長見樓價回少少立即大大力托市，有特區政府香港樓無得輸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abea8d8ea53178c9f233e2aeb82d2cdf0c026e43","tid":1670841,"uid":121265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9239618ecbfa27f28160698e663e5692e4894a36","tid":1670841,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20eea7f39c06cfe8f47c796e4057e06d62a1388f","tid":1670841,"uid":35950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"遲買升多二百萬，到時香港人供得仲苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6da3a0410b6e962653a7049f08572ad53bcf2a3","tid":1670841,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"